{"tid":2240789,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"乘客不滿司機說這次總統會投拜登，竟辱罵司機是「無撚用廢鳩」","createTime":"2020-10-13T02:18:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T03:00:31.000Z","uid":92376,"like":9,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d7b520e2e1993a74f986b06536adf104bf0fea05","tid":2240789,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T02:18:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hovd02GBEp0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fhovd02GBEp0&d=W9k3bdIekjUozLnTtmc2V2DcYOQIx6XO0JIcXsozN2c%3D&h=f42ba9c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hovd02GBEp0</a><br />\n<br />\n影片中駕駛在國外論壇分享了這段影片，他說當天是在凌晨3點多時載到這對夫妻，駕駛表示在兩人上車前，這名男子還站在川普的競選旗幟旁拍照。<br />\n<br />\n載送路程中這名男子問駕駛「這次總統你會投給誰？」，駕駛表示他會投給拜登，結果男子一聽當場變臉，不斷用很差的語氣逼問駕駛為什麼要投給拜登，但由於駕駛並不想讓衝突惡化，所以並沒有正面回答，沒想到這名男子越講越不爽，甚至還威脅駕駛說要「打爆他」，駕駛為了自保才會開始錄影。<br />\n<br />\n事後Uber官方發表聲明表示他們已經檢視了當天的影片，並決定將該名乘客列入「終生禁乘」黑名單，Uber的發言人表示：「我們譴責該位乘客帶有污辱和歧視的談話內容，我們也立即移除了該位乘客的權限，他將永久無法使用Uber的平台服務。」<br />\n<br />\n鬧得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50872049c580e2fb0ee9983d95dcfb77d1e90e48","tid":2240789,"uid":52658,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T02:19:15.000Z","msg":"講事實有咩問題？"},{"pid":"3c40753aabada2719f20fab2ae916291d898eb7c","tid":2240789,"uid":92376,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50872049c580e2fb0ee9983d95dcfb77d1e90e48","tid":2240789,"uid":52658,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T02:19:15.000Z","msg":"講事實有咩問題？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T02:26:16.000Z","msg":"無 uber仲要ban人forever<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe1ec3a07b67fca57dc1ee796bab5eadd675f7c1","tid":2240789,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T03:00:31.000Z","msg":"無人"}]}